{"tid":2303758,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"明日大嶼撥款藏小白象群  勘測喜靈洲790萬元 公眾活動費1,100萬元","createTime":"2020-11-28T08:05:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-28T09:02:32.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"add8b27ea79943ab39c070465f829a00f9969ba4","tid":2303758,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T08:05:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201128/LWLEJJX7SBGKLGGPKCM4XO64GI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201128%2FLWLEJJX7SBGKLGGPKCM4XO64GI%2F&d=xEw7bVcEuEkne8wYN5Y7CnjL6x1fkqqvETpDxuWVMK8%3D&h=c3e6cfc8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201128%2FLWLEJJX7SBGKLGGPKCM4XO64GI%2F&h=cf8cb0a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201128/LWLEJJX7SBGKLGGPKCM4XO64GI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n明日大嶼撥款藏小白象群 <br />\n勘測喜靈洲790萬元 公眾活動費1,100萬元<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/RSZPzZb8jubL3FG1mXWSrydTLjg=/2843x1774/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OSWFMAH3XZAMTF7HJLRNVKRAHA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FRSZPzZb8jubL3FG1mXWSrydTLjg%3D%2F2843x1774%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOSWFMAH3XZAMTF7HJLRNVKRAHA.jpg&h=bb35aeec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】立法會財委會昨正式開始審議明日大嶼前期研究撥款，涉款5.5億元。這項被質疑是無底深潭的超級大白象工程，內裏又包含多個不明所以的小白象；包括政府聲稱是「虛」的長洲南及喜靈洲填海研究費用，涉款790萬元，而單是一項「公眾參與活動」就耗資1,100萬元。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：結合海洋公園 邱騰華：海鮮舫不只食海鮮<br />\n<br />\n根據發展局文件，政府建議在鄰近喜靈洲和長洲南可能劃作人工島的範圍及附近水域收集資料，顧問費連監管工地勘測工程便耗用790萬元。多名議員在會上問及有關項目，發展局長黃偉綸稱，政府暫時沒有相關海域的發展時間表及路線圖，「喜靈洲嗰個係虛嘅，但係對將來有參考價值」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黃偉綸︰研融資補貼成本<br />\n<br />\n撥款細項中又有一項涉及1,100萬元用作「公眾參與活動費用」，黃偉綸辯稱，計劃諮詢範圍較多，數字是參考過往的公眾諮詢工作估算，更反稱「亦有議員擔心會唔會太少，但我哋覺得應該應付到」。<br />\n<br />\n有關計劃的成本。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n多位區議員及民間團體昨早到政府總部請。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n世界自然基金會（WWF）昨早亦有請願行動。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/nfDRqlmT0cCi_BTK2DOd8RRiF2M=/1262x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EQTP7GGGE5FH5AR7QDDXWRDSRI.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FnfDRqlmT0cCi_BTK2DOd8RRiF2M%3D%2F1262x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEQTP7GGGE5FH5AR7QDDXWRDSRI.JPG&h=e000ee31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■WWF昨早到政總抗議明日大嶼破壞大嶼山的自然資源。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/tWY_EkYipAXNAc65nRPZyREBlro=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/R3UJ2B5ZA5CUVPOGYLBBFMLXWA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FtWY_EkYipAXNAc65nRPZyREBlro%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FR3UJ2B5ZA5CUVPOGYLBBFMLXWA.jpg&h=e3705eb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃偉綸"},{"pid":"c2912da517152b3403367cf718f68f4830cb31a2","tid":2303758,"uid":276273,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T08:19:19.000Z","msg":"區議會 D 維穩費過唔到，又巧立名目，呃市民既血汗。<br />\n騙徙手法經常咁做"},{"pid":"6e3b34db5ae1502c6f86d9e2a2e42746a7e03a8e","tid":2303758,"uid":290314,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T08:39:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"566ab54d49646504925bcbe5de8ee098c1690962","tid":2303758,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T09:02:32.000Z","msg":"宣傳費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}